About Robert H. Sands




Practice DescriptionMr. Sands focuses his practice on trials involving complex business litigation matters, including:•Toxic Torts •Product Liability •Commercial Litigation •Personal Injury Litigation •Cybersecurity Mr. Sands has tried cases in both state and federal courts and has represented clients in Illinois, Missouri, California and numerous federal courts throughout the country on behalf of defendants in multi-million dollar litigation, including toxic tort, product liability, transportation, admiralty, class actions, drug and medical device, personal injury, premises liability, medical malpractice, insurance coverage, and bad faith litigation.Mr. Sands serves...
