Pacific Sands Welcomes Robert Vineyard as Pool and Spa Product Sales Manager

Pacific Sands (PFSD) 
ecoONE nontoxic products 

RACINE, WI--(Marketwire - September 20, 2007) - Pacific Sands, Inc. (OTCBB: PFSD) 
is pleased to announce the addition of Robert Vineyard as National Sales 
Manager. Vineyard brings over 20 years' experience in customer service and 
customer-focused selling. His 13 years' experience with DuPont in channel driven 
distribution sales and marketing positions provides Pacific Sands with 
additional expertise for gaining and servicing large accounts. 

"I will take a multi-tiered approach to enhance all selling aspects of Pacific 
Sands' products," said Mr. Vineyard. "Working closely with spa manufacturers, 
distributors, dealers and end users, I envision Pacific Sands, Natural Water 
Technologies as a significant participant in the multi-billion dollar pool and 
spa industry within the next 2 years." 

Mr. Vineyard is the primary contact point for all sales to the pool and spa 
industry. Expanding on the company's core goal of making pool and spa 
maintenance safe and simple, Bob plans to bring equal simplicity to our system 
of product distribution and support for our ecoONE business partners. 

Mr. Vineyard added, "Customers love the products because they are simple, safe, 
effective and environmentally friendly. Our distribution partners enjoy full 
product and marketing support in conjunction with industry leading profit 
margins. Dealers help the environment and enhance customer satisfaction while 
making an excellent margin." 

About Pacific Sands 

Pacific Sands, Inc., promoting earth, health, pet and kid-friendly chemistry 
solutions, is publicly traded on the NASDAQ OTCBB. The company's core ecoONE® 
chlorine free pool, spa and nontoxic household cleaning product lines deliver 
earth, health and kid-safe alternatives. More information:
www.pacificsands.biz 


Dealer inquiries contact: BobV@pacificsandsinc.com. 

ecoONE Products are available on-line from 
www.poolandspa.com, America's leading source for pool covers and pool and 
spa chemicals. 

