Sands Bethlehem Event Center InformationThis is a 14,000 square foot venue known for performing arts and music events, located in Bethlehem, PA. Opened in May of 2009, the venue features seating for 2,250 people. This venue has hosted events for Janet Jackson, Diana Ross, Il Divo, Lewis Black, and Yanni, among other concert, comedy, and theatre events.Box Office Tickets offers tickets to all the best shows. Check above for all available dates and times. Order your tickets online, or you can reach customer service by calling toll-free (1-800-840-9227), or via Live Chat.









